nstruction? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/0183c277cc3076464fa5bfe4511e17a0.avif?t=1773082183\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The snowball effect becomes reality. Smart decisions create synergies that let you conquer ever-stronger waves of enemies and bosses in a firework of effects.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/96625888033782ed4189dfe605c8dcce.avif?t=1773082183\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete globally or with friends in our ranking system. Can you reach the Valhalla rank?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/b849b2e6a4d49bd2b55ebddfa2f33d38.poster.avif?t=1773082183\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/b849b2e6a4d49bd2b55ebddfa2f33d38.webm?t=1773082183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/b849b2e6a4d49bd2b55ebddfa2f33d38.mp4?t=1773082183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
